{"tid":2195242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新鴻基、帝苑逼員工全民檢測","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T15:27:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1cdeff60b283002e3c5a289f1aea582c35c0941","tid":2195242,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/674JVTUTONASDLO55KVBM4NT3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F674JVTUTONASDLO55KVBM4NT3E%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=9298fc60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F674JVTUTONASDLO55KVBM4NT3E%2F&h=9182da42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/674JVTUTONASDLO55KVBM4NT3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新鴻基、帝苑逼員工全民檢測<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1gO2LY_ZMefno4_6F2I9g41vn_A=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EFWXC4JOLJGB3MPLTYQ4W7PWEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1gO2LY_ZMefno4_6F2I9g41vn_A%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEFWXC4JOLJGB3MPLTYQ4W7PWEA.jpg&h=aa19b0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新鴻基屬下帝苑酒店被指強制所有員工參加全民檢測。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全民檢測參與人數比政府預期低，教育局昨向全港官立中學、小學發信，敦促學校呼籲學生、家長及家人，積極參與檢測計劃，聲言可為稍後恢復面授課程締造更有利的條件。新鴻基地產及屬下帝苑酒店亦被指近日下指令，強制所有員工參加全民檢測，若不參加需申報理由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n員工斥為政府篤數<br />\n<br />\n有新鴻基地產職員向本報表示，近日收到公司指令，要求各部門強制接受全民檢測，「公司發現叫同事自願去檢測成效不大，就叫部門強迫我哋去」。新鴻基回覆稱，鼓勵員工參與檢測計劃，員工是否參加純屬自願，而為方便有意參與的員工，可安排員工於工作時間內到就近檢測中心檢測。<br />\n<br />\n帝苑酒店員工張女士（化名）亦指，接獲公司人力資源部電郵，傳達酒店業務部行政總裁的指示，酒店全體員工約527人「務必參與」全民檢測，員工需填報做過檢測的資料、預約時間和不檢測原因。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"00eab051e4497999afe13563b2d682432698ab6e","tid":2195242,"uid":133383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"新鴻基有【黨委】已共產了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35af4447ede2ced63ded87e4615563a6c7117a7b","tid":2195242,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"我公司倒返轉<br />\n話貼錢都一定要員工出去私家驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 外資公司"},{"pid":"74d99dbc1578293ef498c4ed6e5e2a97654120e9","tid":2195242,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"老細話員工檢測免費一日AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}